article_text:
Custer, SD

The 50th Annual Buffalo Roundup in Custer State Park may be over, but people can still hear the thunder in photos from the event.

This year's roundup drew record crowds of over 20,000 people.

Viewers have sent in photos of this year's roundup to remember the record-breaking event.

You can send us photos by uploading them to our gallery, using your mobile app, or sending them to uShare@keloland.com.
